## 1.5.0
- Added configurable automation runner controls (dry-run, continue-on-error, log levels, no-color mode) in shared script utilities.
- Refactored doctor/bootstrap/verify scripts into staged, timed steps with consolidated execution summaries and error traps.
- Added backend packaging sanity checks to verification and introduced Makefile convenience targets for fast/dry-run/verbose workflows.
- Added automation smoke tests for script syntax, dry-run orchestration, and summary behavior.
- Updated usage/documentation examples and semantic version metadata to reflect the new release.
